data.description: Welcome to your new haven of comfort and style! This recently renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, nestled on a charming corner lot, is a true gem waiting for its new owners. Enjoy the warmth of brand-new flooring and the fresh ambiance created by recently painted walls and cabinets. The kitchen is a culinary haven with custom countertops, adding a touch of uniqueness. With an extra flex room, it opens up possibilities for a home office, guest room, or hobby space, catering to your individual lifestyle. Schedule your viewing today and be prepared to fall in love with the perfect combination of quaint charm and contemporary comfort.
